                <updated>Mon, 23 Jan 2012 13:34:46 +0000</updated>
                            <resolved>Mon, 23 Jan 2012 13:34:37 +0000</resolved>
                                                    <fixVersion>Lustre 1.8.7</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="27188" author="adilger" created="Mon, 23 Jan 2012 13:34:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Brian reported in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/1167&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/1167&lt;/a&gt; that this was caused by the Ubuntu/Debian build system on b1_8 being much more particular than on master.  The resolution was to list the new build/checkpatch.pl file in the EXTRA_DIST list of build/autoMakefile.am.toplevel.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
